   "source": [
    "Ridge Regression !\n",
    "$$RSS + \\lambda \\sum_{j=1}^{p} \\beta_j^2$$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "cb7d3788",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "Lasso regression !\n",
    "$$Sum\\ of\\ Errors + \\lambda \\sum_{j=1}^{p} |\\beta_j|$$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "74550c5a",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "Elastic Net !\n",
    "$$Error + \\lambda_1 \\sum |\\beta| + \\lambda_2 \\sum \\beta^2$$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "8bdc6452",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "Hyperparameter Tuning !"
   ]
  }
